{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":556071,"duration_api_ms":206650,"ttft_ms":2600,"num_turns":38,"result":"All verification passes. **US-041 is complete and committed** (`105724a`).\n\n## Summary\n\nImplemented **US-041: 分析型图谱：结构性 gap 检测 + 反思提示** — the \"you wrote about A and B for weeks but never connected them — here's a bridging question\" feature for DayPage Web (Next.js + Postgres/Drizzle). The bulk of the implementation existed from prior iterations; I verified, completed, and committed it.\n\n### How each acceptance criterion is met\n\n1. **社区检测 + 结构性 gap 分析识别'应连未连'的簇对** — `gap-detect.ts` runs **connected-component community detection** (union-find) over the currently-valid page-link graph (`valid_to IS NULL`, reusing US-040's temporal links). It builds embedding centroids per community and finds pairs in a **sweet-spot similarity band** (0.6–0.92: related but not the same topic), each written about over **≥14 days** — clusters that *should* be connected but live in separate components (so guaranteed unlinked).\n\n2. **LLM 生成跨 gap 反思问题 → 写入 inbox_items（新增 kind）** — `generateBridge()` prompts the LLM for a bridging question; results are inserted as `inbox_items` under a **new `gap` enum kind** (schema + migration `0018_us041_inbox_gap_kind.sql`). A sha256 **gap signature** with a 30-day idempotency window prevents re-surfacing the same gap.\n\n3. **用户在 /inbox 看到提示并采纳或忽略** — new `GapCard` in `InboxClient.tsx` renders the two clusters (A ⇄ B pills) and the question, with **Reflect on this** / **Ignore** actions wired to the resolve route (recorded in `resolution`, no destructive side-effect). A \"Gaps\" filter chip and counts were added across `page.tsx`, the list API, and the kind enum.\n\n4. **`pnpm run build` 通过** — ✓ Compiled successfully.\n5. **Typecheck passes** — ✓ `tsc --noEmit` exit 0.\n6. **Browser verification** — dev server booted clean (no compile errors); `/inbox` → 307→login, `POST /api/inbox/gap-detect` → 401 (new route runs), `?kind=gap` accepted. Full authenticated UI walkthrough needs seeded graph data unavailable in this headless env.\n\nAlso added: `POST /api/inbox/gap-detect` for on-demand sweeps, a daily inngest cron (05:00 UTC), and 8 passing unit tests (community detection, gap signature, thresholds).\n\n**Lint note:** `pnpm run lint` reports 10 errors, but linting *only my changed files* yields **0 errors** — all 10 are pre-existing `react-hooks/purity` (`Date.now()` in render) issues in unrelated components (insights/today/chat cards) that this story does not touch.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"1e63dd27-b35b-4256-9cbf-847b90c3059c","total_cost_usd":1.4958269999999998,"usage":{"input_tokens":5059,"cache_creation_input_tokens":46244,"cache_read_input_tokens":1773974,"output_tokens":11727,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":46244,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":993,"cache_read_input_tokens":63412,"cache_creation_input_tokens":311,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":311},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":1265,"outputTokens":16,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.001345,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-opus-4-8":{"inputTokens":5059,"outputTokens":11727,"cacheReadInputTokens":1773974,"cacheCreationInputTokens":46244,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":1.4944819999999999,"contextWindow":1000000,"maxOutputTokens":64000}},"permission_denials":[],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"6ec38179-e9bd-4e07-9af3-eb97306ffb0f"}
